  "time_ut": 1656247958,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Web for abused students",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police have launched a search operation in Mullaitivu in search of three more high school students linked to schoolgirl abuse.",
        "Upon learning of the incident, Mullaitivu police arrested five students, including a private class teacher, on charges of abusing a high school student and possessing nude videos of female students.",
        "A victim student has lodged a complaint at the Mullaitivu Police Station on 18.06.2022 alleging sexual abuse by a private tutor (mathematics subject) teacher in Mullaitivu town.",
        "The suspect, who was recently selected as a development officer who used to go home and teach maths under the name of 'Private Class', has been appointed as a teacher in a primary school in Mullaitivu.",
        "He has been going to students' homes and teaching exclusively math lessons.",
        "Four high school students from Selvavuram, Chilaw, Unnappilavu \u200b\u200band Kallapadu areas were arrested on the 20th and released on bail following a complaint lodged in connection with the incident.",
        "Mullaitivu police have arrested a student friend (18 years old) of Kallappadu South, who was the main culprit in the incident, on the 21st and will be remanded until the 30th.",
        "Investigations have revealed that he took a nude photo of his victim, a schoolgirl, and shared it with a private class teacher and students.",
        "The teacher involved in the incident surrendered to the Mullaitivu District Magistrate's Court on the 23rd through a lawyer. The court also ordered that he be kept in remand till the next 30th.",
        "The cases were taken up in the Mullaitivu District Magistrate's Court in the presence of Judge R. Saravanaraja.",
        "The Mullaitivu Police have arrested six students and handed them over to the Mullaitivu District Hospital Legal Officer for a medical examination.",
        "Police said that the medical examination report of the forensic officer has not been received yet and the report will be submitted to the court.",
        "Mullaitivu police are in the process of arresting three students involved in the incident and the case will be taken up in court on the 30th."
      ],
